269
00:16:45,785 --> 00:16:47,058
Good morning, Mr Darricott.

270
00:17:12,951 --> 00:17:14,096
Good afternoon, sir.

271
00:17:14,918 --> 00:17:15,619
Eugene.

272
00:17:17,452 --> 00:17:19,405
Miss Rachel has been
waiting for you, sir.

273
00:17:20,484 --> 00:17:21,728
She is in the living room.

274
00:17:23,808 --> 00:17:24,728
Thank you.

275
00:17:32,619 --> 00:17:33,974
Hello.
- Well.

276
00:17:35,028 --> 00:17:35,700
Hello.

277
00:17:39,559 --> 00:17:41,106
Well, aren't you glad to see me?

278
00:17:42,084 --> 00:17:42,821
Always.

279
00:17:44,516 --> 00:17:45,752
For the twentieth time ..

280
00:17:45,940 --> 00:17:48,775
